         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Fiji ¶ 19. June 1880 ¶ My dear Sir, ¶  ¶ I am in receipt of your kind note of the 12th April and the 7th of May ¶ Letters not found. ¶  ¶ which were put into my hands a few days ago on my return to of...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">80.06.19</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From John Thurston</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">RB MSS M76, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style=""/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Letterhead motto: 'Esse quam videri' [To be<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>rather than<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>to seem]. MS annotation by M: 'Answ 7/7/80'. Letter not found.</p>
               </note>Fiji</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">19. June 1880</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">My dear Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I am in receipt of your kind note of the 12th April and the 7th of May<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Letters not found.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>which were put into my hands a few days ago on my return to office. It was with very great regret that I failed to see you during my brief stay in Melbourne but indeed I was so overwhelmed with business that I failed to do many things and see many scientific men whom I much desired to meet. For many years I looked forward to meeting you some day and after all I was not so fortunate. A gentleman whom I met at the Club informed me you were to be found at, I think he said a Botanic Museum not far from Government house and one day I drove out there and walked round what seemed a building devoted to some scientific purpose but it was closed — and no one I met could give me information.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>It is just possible I may visit Melbourne at the end of the year and in such case I shall not fail to make my first visit to you —</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The Musa of which on the authority of a settler in Kandavu<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>An island in the Fiji group.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>— I think I wrote to you of a very long one — must I find be a Heleconia but whether described or not remains to be seen —</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The native banana — The "Soaqa" or "Soauka", are I think now flowering and one of my boys shall go into the mountains tomorrow in search. If the 'Suva' were here now I could send you a fine bunch of the fruit. One has flowered in my garden during absence in Australia — I return just to find the fruit ripe —</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>You have obliged me very much with the 'Cinchona' seed — I am trying all I can do to introduce this tree for culture in our mountain districts but so far I have not been lucky — With Cacao I have been most fortunate having established over 3000 trees in two years</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>By this mail I hear with regret of the death of my good friend and correspondent Dr Schaffer<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn3" n="4">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>R. Scheffer. See M to M. Holtze, 7 May 1880.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>of Buitenzorg Java. He rendered me great service with seeds and plants of economic value.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">With renewed thanks</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Believe me my dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Very faithfully yours</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>John B Thurston.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plantnames"
               style="font-style: italic; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Cacao</p>
            <p rend="plantnames"
               style="font-style: italic; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Cinchona<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="plantnames"
               style="font-style: italic; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Musa</p>
         </div>
